                Votis X <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omini</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ostri</ex></expan> Constantini <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> votis X <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omini</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ostri</ex></expan> Licini <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Servandus
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Inschrift befindet sich auf einer Fibel, die in einer Ladung Moselkies unbekannter Herkunft gefunden wurde. Y: Dezennalien Konstantins 315/6, des Licinius 316/7.</p>
            </div>
